OL,3,CRugby club's plea for players as its
OL,4,Cfuture hangs in the balance
OL,6,FAn historic rugby club says it is
OL,7,Ffacing an uncertain future, as it
OL,8,Fstruggles to recruit new members and
OL,9,Fretain existing ones.
OL,11,FThe 151-year-old Ambleside Rugby Club
OL,12,Falmost closed three years ago, and the
OL,13,Fsituation again looks bleak as the
OL,14,Fclub is at risk of having to pull out
OL,15,Fof its league.
OL,17,FIts director of rugby, Andrew Brown,
OL,18,Fclaims the number of second homes in
OL,19,Fthe area means there are not enough
OL,20,Flocals who could join the club's ranks.
