OL,3,CRugby club's plea for players as its
OL,4,Cfuture hangs in the balance
OL,6,FHe told ITV Border: "Post Covid
OL,7,Fthere's probably more holiday homes
OL,8,Fnow. I think (the proportion of
OL,9,Fholiday homes) is at 54%, (the) next
OL,10,Fvillage is 72%. That's part of the
OL,11,Fproblem - employers are having to bus
OL,12,Femployees into the area, because of a
OL,13,Flack of locals."
OL,15,FHead coach Matthew Kaye says that
OL,16,Funiversity students have helped boost
OL,17,Fnumbers, but the club still has to
OL,18,Flook beyond Ambleside to recruit.
