OL,3,CRugby club's plea for players as its
OL,4,Cfuture hangs in the balance
OL,6,FHe said: "It's hard to keep players,
OL,7,Fwe have a really hard place where we
OL,8,Flive. We don't have any local
OL,9,Fpopulation.
OL,11,F"Then we've got the university. We get
OL,12,Fa lot of young players involved, but
OL,13,Fsome of them have never played before.
OL,14,FWe have them, and then we just have to
OL,15,Frally people from further afield."
