OL,3,CRugby club's plea for players as its
OL,4,Cfuture hangs in the balance
OL,6,FMany rugby clubs across the country
OL,7,Fare struggling to put enough players
OL,8,Fon the pitch, but Lake District
OL,9,Fcommunities like Ambleside are facing
OL,10,Fa double threat of second and holiday
OL,11,Fhomes, and rising house prices pushing
OL,12,Fyounger people out of their area.
OL,14,FCllr Will Clark of Westmorland and
OL,15,FFurness Council played rugby at
OL,16,FAmbleside as a child. He fears for the
OL,17,Ffuture of sports more generally should
OL,18,Fclubs like Ambleside continue to
OL,19,Fstruggle.
